               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400106-name-440" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400106-name-440" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400106-name-440" type="surname" value="STURGESS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400106-name-440" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM STURGESS.</persName>
                  </hi>I am a publican, and live in North-street, Fitzroy<lb></lb>square. The prisoner was a fortnight and a few days in my employ, as waiter and potman—on the 25th of October I gave him twenty sovereigns to get changed in the neighbourhood for silver—he did not return—I found him at the station-house last Monday week.</p>
